  "texts": [
    "Most participants expressed that they were making visual encoding and stylistic changes as a customization step in their authoring process.",
    "These customizations were regarded as highly important mainly for communication purposes but sometimes also for personal fulfillment.",
    "Participants often mentioned that aesthetics as part of the customizations were needed so \"people take it more seriously\", as well as \"getting the message across\", i.e., referring to expressiveness and effectiveness.",
    "For example, \"To be honest, if we look at like Nature [or] Cell papers, I think the more impactful papers have better visualizations.",
    "So I think It's also very important that you keep up to this standard, right?\""
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}